---
title: Salmon and Herby Maldon Smashed Potatoes with Roasted Tenderstem® Broccoli and Tomato Butter Sauce
description: Take a bite of this delicious Salmon Parcel, featuring Herby Potatoes smashed with Maldon Salt. These soft, crunchy sea salt flakes contain the perfect balance of natural minerals, offering a fresh intensity and clean taste to enhance the dish. Paired with Roasted Purple Sprouting Broccoli and topped with a Tomato Butter Sauce, this is an extra special recipe that everyone will love.
